,Recommended,255390,35076846,Posted: 19 September,all,Methuselah,"I'm wirting this review early, about what I assume to be 2/3 of the way through the game.I bought this as something appropriate to play with my 6 year old daughter. The game is charming and has no objectionable content whatsoever. I wish there were more games this well made and creative that fit that mold.It's mostly easy but every now and then the puizzles can slow you up for a few minutes. I've never gotten stuck long enough to get frustrated so it balances difficulty with fun (for a somewhat impatient gamer) quite well.My 6 year old is able to play and solve many of the puzzles as well.Great game."
